awardDraw.t.sol
├── when caller is not the owner
│   └── it should revert
└── when caller is the owner
    ├── when randomness request was already sent
    │   └── it should revert with {DRAW_AWARD_DRAW__REQUEST_ALREADY_SENT} error
    └── when randomness request was not already sent
        ├── it should call the {transferAndCall} function of LINK token contract
        ├── it should change the request status to {PENDING}
        ├── it should store the prize for the draw
        ├── it should store the request id made for the draw
        └── it should emit the {RandomnessRequestSent} event
